text: Přibyslav is a town in the Vysočina Region of the Czech Republic. About 4,000 people live there. == Twin towns == Přibyslav is twinned with: * Mook en Middelaar, Netherlands * Sliač, Slovakia == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Towns in the Czech Republic Category:Vysočina Region
